---
import SectionStructure from '../../structures/SectionStructure.astro';
---

<SectionStructure idSection="lets-begin">
  <div class="rounded-md flex flex-col items-center gap-12 xl:px-16 lg:py-12 w-full">
    <span class="text-sm xl:text-base text-[#606773] font-medium">ABOUT THE COMPANY</span>
    <h2 class="Giyaste text-3xl leading-tight tracking-[0.3rem] xl:w-9/12 text-center text-blue lg:text-4xl xl:text-5xl xl:leading-tight xl:font-light xl:tracking-[0.5rem]">
      OUR MISSION AND HISTORY
    </h2>

    <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 lg:flex-row items-center lg:gap-12 xl:gap-20">
      <article class="w-full lg:w-5/12 flex items-center justify-center">
        <p class="text-[#606773] lg:text-lg xl:text-xl">
          Founded with the vision of transforming real estate investment in Dubai, our company is dedicated to guiding clients through every step of their investment journey. From initial inquiries to
          securing the ideal property, we work tirelessly to provide the knowledge, transparency, and expertise you need to invest with confidence.
          <br />
          <br />
          Our team combines years of industry experience and deep local knowledge with a global perspective, ensuring that each client receives personalized guidance and insight. We understand that investing
          in real estate is a major decision, and our mission is to make that decision as informed and rewarding as possible.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="flex flex-col gap-4 justify-center items-center w-full lg:w-6/12 lg:gap-8 lg:justify-center">
        <img src="/public/assets/mission/dubai.png" alt="Mission image" />
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</SectionStructure>
